fields.name: White Bread Rolls
fields.description: Classic white bread rolls, perfect to start your day. Ideal for breakfast or as a side for dinner. Fresh and crispy, baked according to traditional recipe. **Allergens: Gluten, may contain traces of milk and eggs.**

fields.name: Cheese Bread Rolls
fields.description: Savory cheese bread rolls, refined with spicy cheese. A treat at any time of day, whether warm or cold. Perfect for cheese lovers. **Allergens: Gluten, Milk, Eggs.**

fields.name: Raisin Bread Rolls
fields.description: Sweet raisin bread rolls, a classic for young and old. With juicy raisins and a light sweetness. Ideal for coffee or tea. **Allergens: Gluten, may contain traces of milk.**

fields.name: Schwarzbrot (Rye Bread)
fields.description: Hearty rye bread, full-bodied in flavor and rich in fiber. Goes perfectly with savory toppings and soups. **Allergens: Gluten.**

fields.name: White Bread
fields.description: Airy white bread, mild in flavor and versatile. Whether for breakfast, lunch or dinner, white bread is always a good choice. **Allergens: Gluten.**

fields.name: Bauernbrot (Farmhouse Bread)
fields.description: Rustic farmhouse bread, with a strong crust and juicy crumb. A bread like from the countryside, ideal for a hearty snack. **Allergens: Gluten, may contain traces of nuts.**

fields.name: World Champion Bread Rolls
fields.description: World Champion bread rolls, crispy, delicious, simply unbeatable! A roll for true connoisseurs, baked according to a secret recipe. **Allergens: Gluten, Milk.**

fields.name: Pumpkin Seed Bread
fields.description: Pumpkin seed bread, nutty and aromatic, refined with roasted pumpkin seeds. A healthy and tasty bread for every occasion. **Allergens: Gluten, Pumpkin Seeds.**

fields.name: Pretzels
fields.description: Fresh pretzels, the Bavarian classic. Whether pure, with butter or cheese, pretzels are always a treat. Lye pastry at its finest. **Allergens: Gluten.**

fields.name: Quince Bread
fields.description: Quince bread, fruity and sweet, a specialty for the autumn season. Goes perfectly with cheese or simply enjoy pure. **May contain traces of nuts. Gluten-free option available on request.**

fields.name: Christstollen (Christmas Stollen)
fields.description: Juicy Christstollen, filled with raisins, almonds and candied lemon peel. A traditional Christmas pastry that should not be missing on any holiday table. **Allergens: Gluten, Nuts, Milk.**

fields.name: Hutzelbrot (Fruit Bread)
fields.description: Hutzelbrot, a hearty fruit bread with dried pears, plums and nuts. A hearty-sweet treat, especially in the cold season. **Allergens: Gluten, Nuts.**

fields.name: Easter Wreath
fields.description: Festive Easter wreath, a sweet yeast wreath, traditionally baked for Easter and decorated with pearl sugar and almonds. **Allergens: Gluten, Nuts, Eggs, Milk.**

fields.name: Easter Bread
fields.description: Loose Easter bread, a juicy yeast bread that simply belongs to Easter. With fine lemon note and raisins. **Allergens: Gluten, Eggs, Milk.**

fields.name: Wedding Bread
fields.description: Noble wedding bread, a special bread for a special occasion. Festively decorated and of the best quality, for the bridal couple and their guests. **Allergens: Gluten, may contain traces of nuts and milk.**

fields.name: Marble Cake
fields.description: Classic marble cake, juicy and loose, with the typical marble pattern. A cake for every occasion, whether for a birthday or just because. **Allergens: Gluten, Eggs, Milk.**

fields.name: Streusel Cake (Crumb Cake)
fields.description: Crispy streusel cake, with juicy yeast dough and delicious butter streusel. A sheet cake classic that always tastes good. **Allergens: Gluten, Milk.**

fields.name: Black Forest Cherry Cake
fields.description: Tempting Black Forest cherry cake, with juicy cherries, cream and chocolate. The queen of cakes, a treat for all senses. **Allergens: Gluten, Milk, Eggs, may contain traces of nuts.**

fields.name: Danube Wave Cake
fields.description: Popular Danube wave cake, a sheet cake with cherries, chocolate glaze and a creamy buttercream. A classic that is well received at every cake buffet. **Allergens: Gluten, Milk, Eggs.**

fields.name: Bee Sting Cake
fields.description: Creamy bee sting cake, a yeast cake with almonds, honey and a creamy vanilla filling. A German classic that is simply irresistible. **Allergens: Gluten, Nuts, Milk, Eggs.**

fields.name: Strawberry Cream Cake
fields.description: Light strawberry cream cake, with fresh strawberries and fluffy cream. The perfect cake for summer, fruity and refreshing. **Allergens: Gluten, Milk, Eggs.**

fields.name: Plum Cake
fields.description: Juicy plum cake, a sheet cake with fresh plums and crispy streusel. An autumnal delight that tastes good warm and cold. **Allergens: Gluten, Milk.**

fields.name: Baumkuchen (Tree Cake)
fields.description: Noble Baumkuchen, a layer cake that is elaborately handmade. A special pastry for festive occasions. **Allergens: Gluten, Eggs, Milk, Nuts.**

fields.name: Linzer Torte
fields.description: Aromatic Linzer torte, with hazelnuts and redcurrant jam. An Austrian specialty that is particularly popular at coffee time. **Allergens: Gluten, Nuts, Eggs, Milk.**

fields.name: Easter Lamb Cake
fields.description: Lovingly designed Easter lamb cake, a sponge cake in lamb shape that brings joy at Easter. A sweet eye-catcher on the Easter table. **Allergens: Gluten, Eggs, Milk.**

fields.name: Carrot Cake
fields.description: Juicy carrot cake, with carrots, nuts and a cream cheese frosting. A classic that tastes good not only at Easter. **Allergens: Gluten, Nuts, Eggs, Milk.**

fields.name: Birthday Cake
fields.description: Individual birthday cake, designed according to your wishes. Make a birthday an unforgettable experience with a personal cake. **Allergens: Gluten, Eggs, Milk. Please specify any further allergies when ordering.**

fields.name: Birthday Cupcakes
fields.description: Imaginative birthday cupcakes, small cakes that bring great joy. Decorated with colorful sprinkles and toppings, ideal for any birthday party. **Allergens: Gluten, Eggs, Milk.**

fields.name: Wedding Cake
fields.description: Dreamlike wedding cake, multi-tiered and elegant, the highlight of every wedding celebration. Created according to your ideas, for the most beautiful day in life. **Allergens: Gluten, Eggs, Milk. Please specify any further allergies when ordering.**

fields.name: Berliner (Doughnut)
fields.description: Classic Berliners, filled with fruity jam and dusted with powdered sugar. A sweet treat, not only for carnival season. **Allergens: Gluten, Eggs, may contain traces of milk.**

fields.name: Pudding Pocket
fields.description: Puff pastry pudding pocket, filled with creamy vanilla pudding and crispy puff pastry. A sweet snack for in between. **Allergens: Gluten, Milk, Eggs.**

fields.name: Spritzgebäck (Butter Cookies)
fields.description: Delicate Spritzgebäck, crispy and buttery, in various shapes. A popular pastry that is especially popular during Christmas time. **Allergens: Gluten, Milk, Eggs.**

fields.name: Nut Corners
fields.description: Crispy nut corners, with hazelnuts and apricot jam. A sweet classic that is perfect with coffee. **Allergens: Gluten, Nuts, may contain traces of milk.**

fields.name: Weckmann (St. Martin's Day Man)
fields.description: Funny Weckmann, a yeast dough man, traditionally baked for St. Martin's Day. A sweet custom for young and old. **Allergens: Gluten, Eggs, Milk.**

fields.name: Christmas Cookies
fields.description: Diverse Christmas cookies, a colorful mixture of different varieties. Homemade and lovingly decorated, for a festive Advent season. **Allergens: Gluten, Eggs, Milk, Nuts depending on variety.**

fields.name: Gingerbread
fields.description: Spicy gingerbread, with honey and Christmas spices. A traditional Christmas pastry that melts in your mouth. **Allergens: Gluten, may contain traces of nuts and milk.**
